# Intuition
We only need to check the change in delta once, since it's supposed to be the same throughout.

# Approach
This is the monkey approach, basically calculate the delta between our first two points and make sure it never changes. If the x value never changes we just set it to 2^32, the highest possible.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
$$O(n)$$ I think

- Space complexity:
Should be $$O(1)$$ 

# Code
